headline: Lennox L40 Smart Thermostat Named "Smart Thermostat of the Year" in the IoT Breakthrough Awards
summary: Lennox (NYSE: LII) announced that the Lennox® L40 Smart Thermostat has been selected as the "Smart Thermostat of the Year" in the IoT Breakthrough Awards.
